quit            //q
return          //ret
system-view     //sys
display current-configuration            //d cu
display user-interface                   //d user-i

改名
sysname

ip地址
sys
int g 0/0/0
ip address 1.1.1.1 24

设置cnsole
concole接口设置用户级别(0,1,2,3-15)
sys 
user-interface concole 0   //user-i con 0
user privilege level 2     //us p l 2
authentication-mode password
set authentication password cipher 1234    //set a p c 1234



设置vty
vty设置最大连接数量
sys
user-interface maximum-vty 15    //user-i m 15

配置telnet
password模式
user authentication password 1234
//set authentication password cipher 1234

aaa模式
local-user admin password cipher 123123  //l admin p c 123123
//admim是用户名password cipher表示密码用蜜文形式保存123123是密码
local-user admin service-type telnet     //l admin ser tel
q
user-interface vty 0 14          //user-i v 1 14
user privilege level 2           //us p l 2
authentication-mode aaa          //接入类型为用户名密码验证
q


保存配置
save file.zip
自动保存
autosave interval on
autosave interval 1440     //24小时保存一次
autosave interval 00:00:00 //定时保存

startup saved-configuration save.zip  //设置下次启动配置文件
compare configuration                 //比较当前配置文件与下次启动配置文件

ftp传输
配置路由器r1和路由器r2
sys
sysname r1
int g 0/0/0
ip addr 192.168.0.1 24

sys
sysname r2
int g 0/0/0
ip addr 192.168.0.2 24

设置ftp服务器
ftp server enable
set default ftp-directory flash:/
aaa
local-user xjj password cipher 1234
local-user xjj service-type ftp
local-user xjj ftp-dirctory flash:/backup
local-user xjj privilege level 3

r2登陆r1的ftp
ftp 192.168.0.1
xjj
1234
get/put vrpcfg.zip





配置dhcp
dis ip pool查看地址池

基于接口地址池的dhcp
1.dhcp enable
2.dhcp select int

额外dhcp server excluded-ip-addr 192.168.1.1 192.168.1.10
额外dhcp server dhs-list 8.8.8.8
主机dhcp时自动获取dns地址


基于全局dhcp的地址池
dhcp enable
ip pool name1
* network 192.168.1.0         #请求ip的主机所在的网段
* gateway-list 192.168.1.254  #请求ip的主机的路由器的ip地址
* gateway-list 192.168.1.254 mask 24 #如果是远程需要配置子网掩码
lease day 2
excluded-ip-address 192.168.1.250 192.168.1.253
dns-list 8.8.8.8
int g0/0/0
dhcp aelect global



dhcp中继

单个配置
dhcp enable
面向请求ip的主机的接口
dhcp select relay
dhcp relay server-ip dhcp服务器地址

dhcp服务器组配置
dhcp server group name1
dhcp-server dhcp服务器2地址
dhcp-server dhcp服务器1地址
int ///
dhcp select relay
dhcp relay server-select name1
